# Keep the Docker build context small and, critically, never copy the host's
# node_modules into the image — the build stages install their own. Copying the
# host tree (Windows symlinks + host-specific pnpm store) over a container's
# node_modules breaks module resolution (MODULE_NOT_FOUND).

# Dependencies & build output
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.turbo
**/coverage

# Local env & secrets (compose/CI inject these at runtime; never bake into images)
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# VCS, CI, tooling, editor
.git
.gitignore
.github
.vscode
.idea
.claude
.codex

# Playwright / test artifacts
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
**/.playwright
.playwright-mcp

# Docs (not needed to build the apps; includes the large vendored design comp)
docs

# Logs
**/*.log
